{"kanda":6,"sarga":115,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"तेरावणवधंदृष्टवादेवगन्धर्वदानवाः ।जग्मुस्स्वैस्वैर्विमानैस्तेकथयन्तश्शुभाःकथाः","trans":"In the meantime, Devas, Gandharvas, Danavas speaking to each other an auspicious story of Ravana's destruction went in their respective aerial cars.","words":[{"d":"ते","m":"in the meantime"},{"d":"देवगन्धर्वदानवाः","m":"Devas, Gandharvas, Danavasरावणवधम् Ravana's destruction"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"ते","m":"they"},{"d":"कथाः","m":"story"},{"d":"कथयन्तः","m":"speaking to each other"},{"d":"स्वैःस्वैः","m":"their"},{"d":"विमानैः","m":"aerial cars"},{"d":"जग्मुः","m":"went"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"रावणस्यवधंघोरंराघवस्यपराक्रमम् ।सुयुद्धंवानराणां च सुग्रीवस्य च मन्त्रितम् अनुरागं च वीर्यं च सौमित्रेर्लक्ष्मणस्य च ।पतिव्रतात्वंसीतायाहनूमतिपराक्रमम् कथयन्तोमहाभागाजग्मुर्हष्टायथागतम् ।","trans":"Speaking about the highly respected Raghava's prowess, the end of dreadful Ravana, the good fighting of Vanaras, counsel of Sugriva, valour of Hanuman, love of Lakshmana, fidelity of Sita, all rejoiced and returned as they had come.","words":[{"d":"महाभागाः","m":"highly respected"},{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"घोरम्","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"वधम्","m":"end"},{"d":"राघवस्य","m":"Raghava's"},{"d":"पराक्रमम्","m":"prowess"},{"d":"वानराणाम्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"सुयुद्धम्","m":"good fight"},{"d":"सुग्रीवस्य","m":"Sugriva's"},{"d":"मन्त्रितम्","m":"counsel"},{"d":"सौमित्रेः","m":"Saumithri"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणस्य","m":"Lakshmana's"},{"d":"अनुरागं च","m":"love"},{"d":"वीर्यं च","m":"valour"},{"d":"पतिव्रतात्वम्","m":"fidelity of Sita"},{"d":"पराक्रमम्","m":"valiance"},{"d":"कथयन्तः","m":"speaking"},{"d":"यथागतम्","m":"as they had come from"},{"d":"जग्मुः","m":"returned"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"रावणस्यवधंघोरंराघवस्यपराक्रमम् ।सुयुद्धंवानराणां च सुग्रीवस्य च मन्त्रितम् अनुरागं च वीर्यं च सौमित्रेर्लक्ष्मणस्य च ।पतिव्रतात्वंसीतायाहनूमतिपराक्रमम् कथयन्तोमहाभागाजग्मुर्हष्टायथागतम् ।","trans":"Speaking about the highly respected Raghava's prowess, the end of dreadful Ravana, the good fighting of Vanaras, counsel of Sugriva, valour of Hanuman, love of Lakshmana, fidelity of Sita, all rejoiced and returned as they had come.","words":[{"d":"महाभागाः","m":"highly respected"},{"d":"रावणस्य","m":"Ravana's"},{"d":"घोरम्","m":"dreadful"},{"d":"वधम्","m":"end"},{"d":"राघवस्य","m":"Raghava's"},{"d":"पराक्रमम्","m":"prowess"},{"d":"वानराणाम्","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"सुयुद्धम्","m":"good fight"},{"d":"सुग्रीवस्य","m":"Sugriva's"},{"d":"मन्त्रितम्","m":"counsel"},{"d":"सौमित्रेः","m":"Saumithri"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणस्य","m":"Lakshmana's"},{"d":"अनुरागं च","m":"love"},{"d":"वीर्यं च","m":"valour"},{"d":"पतिव्रतात्वम्","m":"fidelity of Sita"},{"d":"पराक्रमम्","m":"valiance"},{"d":"कथयन्तः","m":"speaking"},{"d":"यथागतम्","m":"as they had come from"},{"d":"जग्मुः","m":"returned"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"राघवस्तुरथंदिव्यमिन्द्रदत्तंशिखिप्रभम् अनुज्ञायमहाभागोर्मातलिंप्रत्यपूजयत् ।","trans":"Bidding farewell to Matali joyously, honourable Raghava returned the aerial chariot bestowed to him by Indra.","words":[{"d":"महाभागो","m":"honourable"},{"d":"राघवस्तु","m":"Raghava too"},{"d":"इन्द्रदत्तम्","m":"bestowed by Indra"},{"d":"शिखिप्रभम्","m":"aerial chariot"},{"d":"दिव्यम्","m":"wonderful"},{"d":"रथम्","m":"chariot"},{"d":"अनुज्ञाय","m":"bidding farewell"},{"d":"मातलिम्","m":"Matali"},{"d":"प्रत्यपूजयत्","m":"joyously returned"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"राघवेणाभ्यनुज्ञातोमातलिश्शक्रसारथिः दिव्यंतंरथमास्थायदिवमेवारूरोहसह ।","trans":"Matali, charioteer of Indra too taking Raghava's permission went to heaven in that wonderful chariot.","words":[{"d":"रा:","m":"he"},{"d":"राघवेण","m":"by Raghava"},{"d":"अभ्यनुज्ञातः","m":"with permission"},{"d":"शक्रसारथिः","m":"Indra's charioteer"},{"d":"दिव्यम्","m":"wonderful"},{"d":"तंरथम्","m":"that chariot"},{"d":"आस्थाय","m":"taking"},{"d":"दिवमेव","m":"heaven"},{"d":"आरुरोह","m":"went"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"तस्मिंस्तुदिवमारूढेसुसारथिसन्तमे राघवःपरमप्रीतस्सुग्रीवंपरिषस्वजे ।","trans":"\"On Matali ascending to heaven, Raghava very dearly embraced Sugriva for his help in his victory.\"","words":[{"d":"तस्मिन्","m":"on his"},{"d":"दिवम्","m":"heaven"},{"d":"आरूढे","m":"ascended"},{"d":"सुसारथि","m":"that charioteer"},{"d":"सन्तमे","m":"rejoiced"},{"d":"परमप्रीतः","m":"very dearly"},{"d":"सुग्रीवम्","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"परिषस्वजे","m":"embraced"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"परिष्वज्य च सुग्रीवंलक्ष्मणेनाभिवादितः पूज्यमानोहरिगणैराजगामबलालयम् ।","trans":"On embracing Sugriva, greeted by Lakshmana, and worshipped by the army of Vanaras, Rama returned to the camp.","words":[{"d":"सुग्रीवम्","m":"Sugriva"},{"d":"परिष्वज्य च","m":"embracing"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणेन","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"अभिवादितः","m":"initiated by"},{"d":"हरिगणैः","m":"Vanara troops"},{"d":"पूज्यमानः","m":"worshipped"},{"d":"बलालयम्","m":"by the army"},{"d":"आजगाम","m":"went"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"अथोवाच स काकुत्स्थस्समीपपरिवर्तिनम् सौमित्रिंसत्त्वसम्पन्नंलक्ष्मणंशुभलक्षणम् ।","trans":"And then, Kakuthsa spoke to Saumithri, of auspicious nature and endowed richly with prowess, who stood close by.","words":[{"d":"अथ","m":"and then"},{"d":"सःकाकुत्स्थ:","m":"Kakuthsa"},{"d":"समीपपरिवर्तिनम्","m":"nearby surrounded"},{"d":"सौमित्रिम्","m":"Saumithri"},{"d":"सत्त्वसम्पन्नम्","m":"rich in prowess"},{"d":"शुभलक्षणम्","m":"of auspicious nature"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणम्","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"भीषणमिमंसौम्य लङ्कायामभिषेचय अनुरक्तं च भक्तं च तथापूर्वोपकारिणम् ।","trans":"\"Gentle Lakshmana! Vibheeshana is friendly to me and devoted. He has done me good work in the past. Consecrate him in Lanka.\"","words":[{"d":"सौम्य","m":"gentle"},{"d":"अनुरक्तम्","m":"very friendly"},{"d":"भक्तं च","m":"devotion"},{"d":"तथा","m":"so also"},{"d":"पूर्वोपकारिणम्","m":"done good work in the past"},{"d":"इमम्","m":"him"},{"d":"विभीषणम्","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"लङ्कायाम्","m":"in Lanka"},{"d":"अभिषेचय","m":"consecrate"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"एषमेपरमःकामोयदिमंरावणानुजम् लङ्कायांसौम्य पश्येमभिषिक्तंविभीषणम् ।","trans":"\"O gentle Lakshmana! I desire to see this Vibheeshana, Ravana's brother, consecrated at Lanka\"","words":[{"d":"सौम्य","m":"gentle"},{"d":"एषः","m":"being so"},{"d":"मे","m":"to me"},{"d":"परमः","m":"very"},{"d":"कामः","m":"desire"},{"d":"यत्","m":"that"},{"d":"रावणानुजम्","m":"Ravana's brother"},{"d":"इमंविभीषणम्","m":"this Vibheeshana"},{"d":"लङ्कायाम्","m":"at Lanka"},{"d":"अभिषिक्तम्","m":"consecrate"},{"d":"पश्येयम्","m":"wish to see"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"एवमुक्तस्तुसौमित्रीराघवेणमहात्मना तथेत्युक्त्वासुसम्हृष्टःसौवर्णंघटमाददे ।","trans":"Great selfRaghava having spoken like that, Saumithri, very happily arranged to get a golden vessel.","words":[{"d":"महात्मना","m":"great self"},{"d":"राघवेण","m":"by Raghava"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that manner"},{"d":"उक्तः","m":"spoken"},{"d":"सौमित्रि","m":"Saumithri"},{"d":"तथेति","m":"same way"},{"d":"सुसम्हृष्टः","m":"very happy"},{"d":"सौवर्णम्","m":"golden"},{"d":"घटम्","m":"vessel"},{"d":"आददे","m":"arranged to get"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"तम्घटंवानरेन्द्राणांहस्तेदत्त्वामनोजवान् व्यादिदेशमहासत्त्व: समुद्रसलिलंतदा ।","trans":"Commanded like that, Lakshmana, endowed with mighty prowess placed that vessel in the hands of Vanara chief, who was endowed with the speed of the mind, to get water from the ocean.","words":[{"d":"महासत्त्व:","m":"endowed with mighty prowess"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"तम्","m":"that"},{"d":"घटम्","m":"vessel"},{"d":"वानरेन्द्राणाम्","m":"chief of Vanaras"},{"d":"हस्ते","m":"hand"},{"d":"दत्त्वा","m":"given"},{"d":"मनोजवान्","m":"endowed with speed of mind"},{"d":"समुद्रसलिलम्","m":"water from the ocean"},{"d":"व्यादिदेश","m":"to get"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"अतिशीघ्रंततोगत्वावानरास्तेमनोजवाः आगतास्तुजलंगृह्यसमुद्राद्वानरोत्तमाः ।","trans":"Then the foremost of the Vanaras, endowed with the speed of mind, with all speed went and got water from the ocean.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"मनोजवाः","m":"who has the speed of mind"},{"d":"वानरोत्तमाः","m":"foremost of Vanaras"},{"d":"अतिशीघ्रम्","m":"all speed"},{"d":"गत्त्वा","m":"going"},{"d":"समुद्रात्","m":"ocean's"},{"d":"जलम्","m":"water"},{"d":"गृह्य","m":"taking"},{"d":"आगताः","m":"came"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"ततःस्त्वेकंघटंगृह्यसम्स्थाप्यपरमासने घटेनतेनसौमित्रिरभ्यषिञ्चद्विभीषणम् ।लङ्कायांरक्षसांमध्येराजानंरामशासनात् विधिनामन्त्रदृष्टेनसुहृद्गणसमावृतः ।","trans":"Vibheeshana was made to sit on an excellent seat, surrounded by hosts of friends and dear ones. Thereafter, in the midst of Rakshasas chanting sacred verses in accordance with scriptures, Saumithri took a vessel of water and duly consecrated Vibhishana with the water in the vessel as commanded by Rama, in Lanka.","words":[{"d":"सौमित्रिः","m":"Saumithri"},{"d":"सुहृद्गणसमावृतः","m":"surrounded by hosts of friends and dear"},{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"एकम्","m":"one"},{"d":"घटम्","m":"vessel"},{"d":"गृह्य","m":"taking"},{"d":"विभीषणम्","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"परमासने","m":"excellent seat"},{"d":"संस्थाप्य","m":"making to sit"},{"d":"तेन","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"घटेन","m":"with the vessel"},{"d":"रक्षसाम्","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"मध्ये","m":"midst"},{"d":"मन्त्रदृष्टेन","m":"chanting sacred verses"},{"d":"विधिना","m":"in accordance with scriptures"},{"d":"रामशासनात्","m":"by Rama's command"},{"d":"लङ्कायाम्","m":"in Lanka"},{"d":"राजानम्","m":"kingdom"},{"d":"अभ्यषिञ्चत्","m":"consecrated"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"ततःस्त्वेकंघटंगृह्यसम्स्थाप्यपरमासने घटेनतेनसौमित्रिरभ्यषिञ्चद्विभीषणम् ।लङ्कायांरक्षसांमध्येराजानंरामशासनात् विधिनामन्त्रदृष्टेनसुहृद्गणसमावृतः ।","trans":"Vibheeshana was made to sit on an excellent seat, surrounded by hosts of friends and dear ones. Thereafter, in the midst of Rakshasas chanting sacred verses in accordance with scriptures, Saumithri took a vessel of water and duly consecrated Vibhishana with the water in the vessel as commanded by Rama, in Lanka.","words":[{"d":"सौमित्रिः","m":"Saumithri"},{"d":"सुहृद्गणसमावृतः","m":"surrounded by hosts of friends and dear"},{"d":"ततः","m":"then"},{"d":"एकम्","m":"one"},{"d":"घटम्","m":"vessel"},{"d":"गृह्य","m":"taking"},{"d":"विभीषणम्","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"परमासने","m":"excellent seat"},{"d":"संस्थाप्य","m":"making to sit"},{"d":"तेन","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"घटेन","m":"with the vessel"},{"d":"रक्षसाम्","m":"Rakshasa"},{"d":"मध्ये","m":"midst"},{"d":"मन्त्रदृष्टेन","m":"chanting sacred verses"},{"d":"विधिना","m":"in accordance with scriptures"},{"d":"रामशासनात्","m":"by Rama's command"},{"d":"लङ्कायाम्","m":"in Lanka"},{"d":"राजानम्","m":"kingdom"},{"d":"अभ्यषिञ्चत्","m":"consecrated"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"अभ्यषिञ्चंस्तदासर्वेराक्षसावानरास्तथा प्रहर्षमतुलंगत्वातुष्टुवूराममवे ह ।","trans":"Thereafter all the Rakshasas and Vanaras also consecrated with extreme joy and paid tribute to Rama alone.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"सर्वे","m":"all"},{"d":"राक्षसाः","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"स्तथा","m":"like that"},{"d":"वानराः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"अभ्यषिञ्चन्","m":"consecrated"},{"d":"अतुलम्","m":"extreme"},{"d":"प्रहर्षम्","m":"joy"},{"d":"गत्वा","m":"went"},{"d":"राममेवहि","m":"Rama alone"},{"d":"तुष्टुवुः","m":"paid tribute"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"तस्यामात्याजहृषिरेभक्तायेचास्यराक्षसाः दृष्टवाभिषिक्तंलङ्कायांराक्षसेन्द्रंविभीषणम् ।","trans":"Seeing Vibheeshana consecrated and becoming a king of Lanka, all his ministers and devotees felt rejoiced.","words":[{"d":"लङ्कायाम्","m":"in Lanka"},{"d":"अभिषिक्तम्","m":"consecrated"},{"d":"राक्षसेन्द्रम्","m":"Rakshasa king"},{"d":"विभीषणम्","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"तस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"अमात्याः","m":"ministers"},{"d":"अस्य","m":"his"},{"d":"भक्ताः","m":"devotees"},{"d":"येराक्षसाः","m":"this Rakshasa"},{"d":"जहृषिरे","m":"felt rejoiced"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"राघवःपरमांप्रीतिंजगामसहलक्ष्मणः स तद्राज्यंमहत्प्राप्यरामदत्तंविभीषणः ।","trans":"Vibheeshana felt extreme felicity for attaining the kingdom given by great Rama with Lakshmana.","words":[{"d":"सहलक्ष्मणः","m":"with Lakshmana"},{"d":"राघवः","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"परमाम्","m":"extreme"},{"d":"प्रीतिम्","m":"felicity"},{"d":"जगाम","m":"felt"},{"d":"सः","m":"he"},{"d":"विभीषणः"