य","m":"gentle"},{"d":"महाराजम्","m":"great king"},{"d":"इमम्","m":"this"},{"d":"विभीषणम्","m":"Vibheeshana"},{"d":"अनुज्ञाप्य","m":"with permission"},{"d":"लङ्कांनगरीम्","m":"Lanka city"},{"d":"प्रविश्य","m":"entering"},{"d":"मैथिलीम्","m":"Mythili"},{"d":"कौशलम्","m":"wellbeing"},{"d":"ब्रूहि","m":"enquire"}]},{"v":25,"dev":"वैदेह्यैमांकुशलिनंसुग्रीवं च सलक्ष्मणम् आचक्ष्ववदतांश्रेष्ठरावणं च हतंरणे ।","trans":"\"Convey to Vaidehi that me and Lakshman and also Sugriva are doing well, and that Ravana has been killed, O Best among the eloquent.\"","words":[{"d":"वदताम्","m":"eloquent"},{"d":"श्रेष्ठ","m":"best"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"सलक्ष्मणम्","m":"and Lakshmana"},{"d":"सुग्रीवं च","m":"and Sugriva"},{"d":"कुशलिनम्","m":"are doing well"},{"d":"रावणम्","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"रणे","m":"in combat"},{"d":"हतम्","m":"killed"},{"d":"वैदेह्यै","m":"Vaidehi"},{"d":"आचक्ष्व","m":"tell her"}]}]}